'''Throwing stars''' were sharp, five-pointed pieces of metal which resembled a star.

[[Kharys]] used this weapon when she attacked [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Skye/Legends|Skye]].

